User:
1. UserId
2. Username
3. Password
4. Books issued
5. Account Balance
6. Phone Number
7. Email
8. Address

User Actions :
1. Add new User
2. Issue new book to a user
3. Return a book / book lost / book damaged
4. Retrieve user information:
    i. Name
    ii. Phone number, Email, Address
    iii. Books issued
    iv. Account Balance
5. Change user information
    i. Phone Number, Email, Address
    iv. Account balance



Books:
1. BookId
2. Book Name
3. Book Author
4. Book Publisher
5. Availability
6. Book review /Stars

Book Actions:
1. Add a new Book
2. Mark a book damaged
3. Mark a book lost
4. Book Condition

